Q. What makes this sunscreen different from regular sunscreens?

This is a Korean-inspired sunscreen mousse, not a cream or lotion. It has an ultra-light, airy texture that melts instantly into the skin, leaves zero white cast, and feels like second skin.

Q. Is SPF70++ safe for daily use?

Yes. SPF70++ provides high-level protection from both UVA and UVB rays and is safe for everyday use, especially in Indian weather where sun exposure is intense.

Q. Does it leave any white cast or greasy feel?

Not at all. The mousse blends seamlessly, leaves no white cast, and settles into a soft, velvety finish. No greasiness. No heaviness.

Q. Can I use it under makeup?

Absolutely. It works beautifully as a makeup base. You can either apply it before makeup or mix it directly with your foundation for a smooth, airbrushed look.

Q. Is this sunscreen suitable for oily and acne-prone skin?

Yes. Its lightweight mousse texture makes it ideal for oily and combination skin. It does not clog pores and feels breathable throughout the day.

Q. Is it suitable for dry skin?

Yes. It hydrates the skin while protecting it from sun damage, making it suitable for dry skin as well.










